講返澳州個case <br />\n英國皇室名義上派咗個總督（由澳洲總理提名）去澳洲<br />\n點解話名義上 因為基本上都係澳洲嗰邊提名<br />\n英國王室就唔會唔say yes 嘅<br />\n呢個總督係有好大權<br />\n憲法賦予佢制定同取消法律<br />\n任免國會議員、各內閣成員甚至總理<br />\n由於西敏制嘅傳統係有權唔多用<br />\n所以如同其他議會制國家一樣<br />\n只係一個虛位元首<br />\n係憲政危機上先會有比較重要既<br />\n例如1975年嗰單<br />\n<br />\n所以假設皇室突然間痴撚咗線<br />\n收返實際嘅任命權<br />\n派條友去做樓主既嘢<br />\n係可以既<br />\n但係呢個政治危機後果係非常大<br />\n作為主權國<br />\n而澳洲只要立即脫離英聯邦修改憲法<br />\n已經可以即時趕這班人走<br />\n所以係唔會發生既"},{"pid":"d0536c2924dc8efcddb40917a172dddbbd4c877a","tid":986844,"uid":109102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9b750a4c71ca2ade2285b4fba4953f4b160283b","tid":986844,"uid":82640,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d30be0546f0918a96d0c45984b438452807c6539","tid":986844,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T04:06:49.000Z","msg":"佢咁做，咪澳加妞一齊廢左國家元首英王，改行總理／總統制。<br />\n我記得睇沈旭暉d文話，十幾年英女王訪澳，澳洲總理走搞9女王，女王都唔能表示乜野，英國早就冇晒對外控制力啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T04:12:14.000Z","msg":"然後霍華德出醜聞再交唔到棒收埋皮<br />\n你估冇關係架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T04:37:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.smh.com.au/world/europe/australia-s-position-on-a-republic-untenable-queen-elizabeth-ii-believes-20181017-p50a2x.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smh.com.au%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Faustralia-s-position-on-a-republic-untenable-queen-elizabeth-ii-believes-20181017-p50a2x.html&d=MrnPEmDsmOOM%2FL8nCE2VhJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=d355c1df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.smh.com.au/world/europe/australia-s-position-on-a-republic-untenable-queen-elizabeth-ii-believes-20181017-p50a2x.html</a><br />\n但係而家事頭婆話要republic就去快<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0349078ed2e5ba38c4df5ae94bfdb5385b3caf37","tid":986844,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d30be0546f0918a96d0c45984b438452807c6539","tid":986844,"uid":129739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":